{
  "video_id": "TvcNw4F0Y4Y",
  "title": "Why you should know how much your coworkers get paid | David Burkus",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13178.0,
      "end_time": 14590.0,
      "text": "How much do you get paid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15155.0,
      "end_time": 17430.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t answer that out loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17666.0,
      "end_time": 19447.0,
      "text": "But put a number in your head."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20170.0,
      "end_time": 24660.0,
      "text": "Now: How much do you think the person sitting next to you gets paid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25176.0,
      "end_time": 27334.0,
      "text": "Again, don&#39;t answer out loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27359.0,
      "end_time": 28461.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29144.0,
      "end_time": 31502.0,
      "text": "At work, how much do you think"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31526.0,
      "end_time": 35464.0,
      "text": "the person sitting in the cubicle or the desk next to you gets paid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35488.0,
      "end_time": 36643.0,
      "text": "Do you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36977.0,
      "end_time": 38342.0,
      "text": "Should you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38961.0,
      "end_time": 42937.0,
      "text": "Notice, it&#39;s a little uncomfortable for me to even ask you those questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42962.0,
      "end_time": 46112.0,
      "text": "But admit it -- you kind of want to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46993.0,
      "end_time": 50518.0,
      "text": "Most of us are uncomfortable with the idea of broadcasting our salary."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50542.0,
      "end_time": 52691.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not supposed to tell our neighbors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52715.0,
      "end_time": 55907.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re definitely not supposed to tell our office neighbors."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55931.0,
      "end_time": 59445.0,
      "text": "The assumed reason is that if everybody knew what everybody got paid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59469.0,
      "end_time": 61259.0,
      "text": "then all hell would break loose."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61283.0,
      "end_time": 63384.0,
      "text": "There&#39;d be arguments, there&#39;d be fights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63408.0,
      "end_time": 65597.0,
      "text": "there might even be a few people who quit."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65621.0,
      "end_time": 69399.0,
      "text": "But what if secrecy is actually the reason for all that strife?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69424.0,
      "end_time": 72420.0,
      "text": "And what would happen if we removed that secrecy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72599.0,
      "end_time": 76590.0,
      "text": "What if openness actually increased the sense of fairness and collaboration"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76614.0,
      "end_time": 77836.0,
      "text": "inside a company?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77860.0,
      "end_time": 81446.0,
      "text": "What would happen if we had total pay transparency?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82254.0,
      "end_time": 83571.0,
      "text": "For the past several years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83595.0,
      "end_time": 86508.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been studying the corporate and entrepreneurial leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86532.0,
      "end_time": 90810.0,
      "text": "who question the conventional wisdom about how to run a company."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90105.0,
      "end_time": 92557.0,
      "text": "And the question of pay keeps coming up."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93105.0,
      "end_time": 95555.0,
      "text": "And the answers keep surprising."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96458.0,
      "end_time": 98265.0,
      "text": "It turns out that pay transparency --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98289.0,
      "end_time": 100399.0,
      "text": "sharing salaries openly across a company --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100423.0,
      "end_time": 103720.0,
      "text": "makes for a better workplace for both the employee"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103960.0,
      "end_time": 104683.0,
      "text": "and for the organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105362.0,
      "end_time": 108461.0,
      "text": "When people don&#39;t know how their pay compares to their peers&#39;,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 108485.0,
      "end_time": 110301.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re more likely to feel underpaid"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110325.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "and maybe even discriminated against."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112646.0,
      "end_time": 115221.0,
      "text": "Do you want to work at a place that tolerates the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115245.0,
      "end_time": 118490.0,
      "text": "that you feel underpaid or discriminated against?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118697.0,
      "end_time": 121207.0,
      "text": "But keeping salaries secret does exactly that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121231.0,
      "end_time": 124113.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a practice as old as it is common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124674.0,
      "end_time": 126766.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126790.0,
      "end_time": 130240.0,
      "text": "the law protects an employee&#39;s right to discuss their pay."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131417.0,
      "end_time": 133975.0,
      "text": "In one famous example from decades ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133999.0,
      "end_time": 136105.0,
      "text": "the management of Vanity Fair magazine"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136129.0,
      "end_time": 138249.0,
      "text": "actually circulated a memo entitled:"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138273.0,
      "end_time": 141478.0,
      "text": "\"Forbidding Discussion Among Employees of Salary Received.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141502.0,
      "end_time": 144824.0,
      "text": "\"Forbidding\" discussion among employees of salary received."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145482.0,
      "end_time": 147629.0,
      "text": "Now that memo didn&#39;t sit well with everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147653.0,
      "end_time": 149698.0,
      "text": "New York literary figures Dorothy Parker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149723.0,
      "end_time": 151485.0,
      "text": "Robert Benchley and Robert Sherwood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151509.0,
      "end_time": 153950.0,
      "text": "all writers in the Algonquin Round Table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153974.0,
      "end_time": 155755.0,
      "text": "decided to stand up for transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155779.0,
      "end_time": 157511.0,
      "text": "and showed up for work the next day"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157535.0,
      "end_time": 160749.0,
      "text": "with their salary written on signs hanging from their neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160773.0,
      "end_time": 162321.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 162716.0,
      "end_time": 164291.0,
      "text": "Imagine showing up for work"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164315.0,
      "end_time": 167805.0,
      "text": "with your salary just written across your chest for all to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169573.0,
      "end_time": 172843.0,
      "text": "But why would a company even want to discourage salary discussions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172867.0,
      "end_time": 176198.0,
      "text": "Why do some people go along with it, while others revolt against it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177906.0,
      "end_time": 180950.0,
      "text": "It turns out that in addition to the assumed reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180974.0,
      "end_time": 184277.0,
      "text": "pay secrecy is actually a way to save a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184301.0,
      "end_time": 186212.0,
      "text": "You see, keeping salaries secret"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186236.0,
      "end_time": 189186.0,
      "text": "leads to what economists call \"information asymmetry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189211.0,
      "end_time": 191482.0,
      "text": "This is a situation where, in a negotiation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191506.0,
      "end_time": 194504.0,
      "text": "one party has loads more information than the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194887.0,
      "end_time": 198297.0,
      "text": "And in hiring or promotion or annual raise discussions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 198321.0,
      "end_time": 201978.0,
      "text": "an employer can use that secrecy to save a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 202518.0,
      "end_time": 205142.0,
      "text": "Imagine how much better you could negotiate for a raise"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 205166.0,
      "end_time": 206972.0,
      "text": "if you knew everybody&#39;s salary."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209612.0,
      "end_time": 212530.0,
      "text": "Economists warn that information asymmetry"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212770.0,
      "end_time": 213724.0,
      "text": "can cause markets to go awry."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213748.0,
      "end_time": 215654.0,
      "text": "Someone leaves a pay stub on the copier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215678.0,
      "end_time": 218960.0,
      "text": "and suddenly everybody is shouting at each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218866.0,
      "end_time": 220572.0,
      "text": "In fact, they even warn"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220596.0,
      "end_time": 225413.0,
      "text": "that information asymmetry can lead to a total market failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226950.0,
      "end_time": 228109.0,
      "text": "And I think we&#39;re almost there."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228133.0,
      "end_time": 229299.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s why:"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 229323.0,
      "end_time": 234251.0,
      "text": "first, most employees have no idea how their pay compares to their peers&#39;."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 234834.0,
      "end_time": 238684.0,
      "text": "In a 2015 survey of 70,000 employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238708.0,
      "end_time": 242890.0,
      "text": "two-thirds of everyone who is paid at the market rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 242113.0,
      "end_time": 244345.0,
      "text": "said that they felt they were underpaid."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 245360.0,
      "end_time": 247915.0,
      "text": "And of everybody who felt that they were underpaid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 247939.0,
      "end_time": 250892.0,
      "text": "60 percent said that they intended to quit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 250916.0,
      "end_time": 253804.0,
      "text": "regardless of where they were -- underpaid, overpaid"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 253828.0,
      "end_time": 255407.0,
      "text": "or right at the market rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 256200.0,
      "end_time": 258659.0,
      "text": "If you were part of this survey, what would you say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 258684.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259960.00000000003,
      "text": "Are you underpaid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259983.0,
      "end_time": 262308.0,
      "text": "Well, wait -- how do you even know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 262333.0,
      "end_time": 264466.0,
      "text": "because you&#39;re not allowed to talk about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 264911.0,
      "end_time": 268510.0,
      "text": "Next, information asymmetry, pay secrecy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268534.0,
      "end_time": 271313.0,
      "text": "makes it easier to ignore the discrimination"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 271337.0,
      "end_time": 273804.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s already present in the market today."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 274217.0,
      "end_time": 277914.0,
      "text": "In a 2011 report from the Institute for Women&#39;s Policy Research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 277938.0,
      "end_time": 280620.0,
      "text": "the gender wage gap between men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 280860.0,
      "end_time": 281824.0,
      "text": "was 23 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 282451.0,
      "end_time": 285700.0,
      "text": "This is where that 77 cents on the dollar comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 285641.0,
      "end_time": 287104.0,
      "text": "But in the Federal Government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 287128.0,
      "end_time": 289191.0,
      "text": "where salaries are pinned to certain levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 289215.0,
      "end_time": 291255.0,
      "text": "and everybody knows what those levels are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 291279.0,
      "end_time": 293364.0,
      "text": "the gender wage gap shrinks to 11 percent --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 293388.0,
      "end_time": 295964.0,
      "text": "and this is before controlling for any of the factors"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 295988.0,
      "end_time": 298881.0,
      "text": "that economists argue over whether or not to control for."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 299264.0,
      "end_time": 301936.0,
      "text": "If we really want to close the gender wage gap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 301960.0,
      "end_time": 304448.0,
      "text": "maybe we should start by opening up the payroll."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 304864.0,
      "end_time": 308850.0,
      "text": "If this is what total market failure looks like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 308110.0,
      "end_time": 311378.0,
      "text": "then openness remains the only way to ensure fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 312274.0,
      "end_time": 314775.0,
      "text": "Now, I realize that letting people know what you make"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 314799.0,
      "end_time": 316445.0,
      "text": "might feel uncomfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 316469.0,
      "end_time": 317984.0,
      "text": "but isn&#39;t it less uncomfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 318800.0,
      "end_time": 320888.0,
      "text": "than always wondering if you&#39;re being discriminated against,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 320912.0,
      "end_time": 324674.0,
      "text": "or if your wife or your daughter or your sister is being paid unfairly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 325353.0,
      "end_time": 329293.0,
      "text": "Openness remains the best way to ensure fairness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 329317.0,
      "end_time": 331230.0,
      "text": "and pay transparency does that."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 331991.0,
      "end_time": 334671.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why entrepreneurial leaders and corporate leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 334695.0,
      "end_time": 337488.0,
      "text": "have been experimenting with sharing salaries for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 337512.0,
      "end_time": 338925.0,
      "text": "Like Dane Atkinson."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 338949.0,
      "end_time": 342828.0,
      "text": "Dane is a serial entrepreneur who started many companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 342852.0,
      "end_time": 344433.0,
      "text": "in a pay secrecy condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 344458.0,
      "end_time": 347811.0,
      "text": "and even used that condition to pay two equally qualified people"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 347835.0,
      "end_time": 349531.0,
      "text": "dramatically different salaries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 349555.0,
      "end_time": 351724.0,
      "text": "depending on how well they could negotiate."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 352910.0,
      "end_time": 355422.0,
      "text": "And Dane saw the strife that happened as a result of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 355888.0,
      "end_time": 358114.0,
      "text": "So when he started his newest company, SumAll,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 358139.0,
      "end_time": 361249.0,
      "text": "he committed to salary transparency from the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 361821.0,
      "end_time": 363559.0,
      "text": "And the results have been amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 364424.0,
      "end_time": 366460.0,
      "text": "And in study after study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 366700.0,
      "end_time": 367945.0,
      "text": "when people know how they&#39;re being paid"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 367970.0,
      "end_time": 369999.0,
      "text": "and how that pay compares to their peers&#39;,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 370230.0,
      "end_time": 372956.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re more likely to work hard to improve their performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 372980.0,
      "end_time": 375829.0,
      "text": "more likely to be engaged, and they&#39;re less likely to quit."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 375853.0,
      "end_time": 377255.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why Dane&#39;s not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 377279.0,
      "end_time": 379450.0,
      "text": "From technology start-ups like Buffer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 379915.0,
      "end_time": 383261.0,
      "text": "to the tens of thousands of employees at Whole Foods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 383285.0,
      "end_time": 386452.0,
      "text": "where not only is your salary available for everyone to see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 386476.0,
      "end_time": 389476.0,
      "text": "but the performance data for the store and for your department"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 389500.0,
      "end_time": 391419.0,
      "text": "is available on the company intranet"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 391443.0,
      "end_time": 392664.0,
      "text": "for all to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 393985.0,
      "end_time": 396447.0,
      "text": "Now, pay transparency takes a lot of forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 396471.0,
      "end_time": 398690.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not one size fits all."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 398930.0,
      "end_time": 400589.0,
      "text": "Some post their salaries for all to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 400613.0,
      "end_time": 402914.0,
      "text": "Some only keep it inside the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 402938.0,
      "end_time": 405522.0,
      "text": "Some post the formula for calculating pay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 405547.0,
      "end_time": 407321.0,
      "text": "and others post the pay levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 407345.0,
      "end_time": 409123.0,
      "text": "and affix everybody to that level."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 409147.0,
      "end_time": 411195.0,
      "text": "So you don&#39;t have to make signs"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 411220.0,
      "end_time": 413744.0,
      "text": "for all of your employees to wear around the office."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 413768.0,
      "end_time": 416681.0,
      "text": "And you don&#39;t have to be the only one wearing a sign"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 416706.0,
      "end_time": 417928.0,
      "text": "that you made at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 418494.0,
      "end_time": 421698.0,
      "text": "But we can all take greater steps towards pay transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 422233.0,
      "end_time": 424261.0,
      "text": "For those of you that have the authority"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 424285.0,
      "end_time": 426790.0,
      "text": "to move forward towards transparency:"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 426103.0,
      "end_time": 427578.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s time to move forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 427943.0,
      "end_time": 430411.0,
      "text": "And for those of you that don&#39;t have that authority:"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 430435.0,
      "end_time": 432414.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s time to stand up for your right to."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 433263.0,
      "end_time": 434988.0,
      "text": "So how much do you get paid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 436186.0,
      "end_time": 438813.0,
      "text": "And how does that compare to the people you work with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 439190.0,
      "end_time": 440496.0,
      "text": "You should know."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 441312.0,
      "end_time": 442587.0,
      "text": "And so should they."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 443936.0,
      "end_time": 445104.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 445128.0,
      "end_time": 448306.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}